headline: O.C. Tanner Celebrates Leading Clients with the 2025 Breakthrough Awards
summary: SALT LAKE CITY, September 12, 2025--O.C. Tanner, the global leader in employee recognition and workplace culture solutions, announced the recipients of the 2025 Breakthrough Awards at the company’s ninth annual employee recognition and workplace culture conference, Influence Greatness in Salt Lake City, Utah. The awards recognized leading organizations from O.C. Tanner’s customers that are elevating workplace culture through the power of recognition.
